## ğŸ§ª Quick Start

### Basic Style

```python
import easygui as gui

app = gui.App("My App")
app.text("Hello World!")
app.button("Click me!", lambda: print("Clicked!"))
app.run()
```

### Decorator Style

```python
import easygui as gui

@gui.app("My App")
def my_app():
    gui.text("Welcome!")
    gui.button("OK", gui.close)
```

